        </header>

        <main class="readme-body">
            <div class="banner-container">
                <p class="banner-text">This is a banner! ✨</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-section">
                <h1>Welcome to the Hero Section!</h1>
                <p>This is a brief and engaging description of what this page is all about. It's designed to capture attention and provide key information at a glance.</p>
                <a href="/projects/index" class="cta-button">View My Work</a>
            </div>

            <section class="about-me-section">
                <div class="profile-card" id="profile-card">
                    <div class="profile-main-info">
                        <div class="profile-header">
